# Generated Android project.
# The Gradle project under src-tauri/gen/android is generated by
# `cargo tauri android init`. It is regenerated from tauri.conf.json, so we do
# not track it wholesale; only intentional edits (e.g. minSdk) are force-added.
#
# Force-tracked native edits (added via `git add -f` — a `!` negative pattern
# cannot re-include files under an ignored dir, so `-f` is the only mechanism).
# Do NOT clean these; re-apply after `tauri android init` per docs/ANDROID-BUILD.md:
#   src-tauri/gen/android/app/src/main/java/com/pillowtome/app/MainActivity.kt
#   src-tauri/gen/android/app/src/main/java/com/pillowtome/app/SuppressSelectionActionModeFrameLayout.kt
/src-tauri/gen/android
/src-tauri/gen/apple

